<br>
For those who want a finishing mob that can be killed with one group of people, they can camp it in Skyfire. For those who don't want to deal with a month long camp in Skyfire and have the backing of a strong guild, they should be able to spawn a harder mob to kill. This mob could perhaps be on the scale of Aaryonar or Lendiniara or something.<br>
<br>
Let's face it, for high end guilds, the stats on the Cleric epic are not overly impressive, and indeed there are many items which have the same or better stats. All guilds still want cleric epics however because of their ability to ress raids quickly.<br>
<br>
For this reason the Cleric epic is still in high demand, and as a result, something needs to be done to make it so that it does not involve such a ridiculous camp. No other epic involves queuing like the Cleric epic does.<br>
<br>
Thun <p><CENTER>
