<br>
Can you say Burn Teams? Ya, I bet the MQ sell price of those items will be pretty high. This solution will prolly make the lower end guilds have to buy the items as the higher guild will be farming them to &quot;epic&quot; all of their clerics and alts. <br>
<br>
